---
title: Tooltip Directions
description: Tooltips pointing top, right, bottom, and left using `::before` and `::after` pseudo-elements.
slug: tooltip-directions
cssFile: tooltip-directions.css
explanation: "The tooltip bubble (`::before`) and arrow (`::after`) are positioned relative to the trigger element using a combination of `top`, `bottom`, `left`, `right`, and `translate`. Each direction shifts the bubble to the appropriate side. The arrow is created by a zero-size element with colored borders — only one border has color, the rest are transparent, forming a triangle pointing toward the trigger. A slide-in `transform` transition adds polish."
---
{% extends "example.njk" %}
{% block demo %}
<div class="td-grid">
	<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip above" data-pos="top">Top ↑</span>
	<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip to the right" data-pos="right">Right →</span>
	<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip below" data-pos="bottom">Bottom ↓</span>
	<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip to the left" data-pos="left">← Left</span>
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block html_code %}
{%- highlight "html" %}
<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip text" data-pos="top">Hover me</span>
<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip text" data-pos="right">Hover me</span>
<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip text" data-pos="bottom">Hover me</span>
<span class="td-tip" data-tip="Tooltip text" data-pos="left">Hover me</span>
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}

{% block css_code %}
{%- highlight "css" %}
.td-tip::before {
  content: attr(data-tip);
  position: absolute;
  background: var(--text);
  color: var(--bg);
  padding: .35rem .65rem;
  border-radius: 6px;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity .2s, transform .2s;
}

/* Top */
[data-pos="top"]::before {
  bottom: calc(100% + 8px);
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(4px);
}
[data-pos="top"]:hover::before {
  transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
  opacity: 1;
}
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}
